data.description: MASSIVE SINGLE STORY!! offers a comfortable living experience with its 4 bedrooms & study, providing plenty of room for relaxation & productivity. Alongside the 3 car garage, there is also a formal dining area, making it an ideal choice for individuals who enjoy cooking & entertaining. Located on an oversized lot, this property boasts a backyard playground. There is another playground conveniently located across the street. Located within the highly sought-after Prosper ISD, this home is part of the Light Farms community, which offers a range of amenities such as hiking & biking trails, an elementary school within the community, a restaurant, resort-style pools, & more. Perfect fit for families & those seeking an active lifestyle.
